//To create user in linux 

$ sudo adduser <enter name of user>

// To add user in groups 

$ sudo usermod -a -G groupname <username>

//to check current user

$ whoami

// To encrypt the file with ccrypt

$ sudo apt-get install ccrypt
$ ccrypt <filename>

enter the encryptin twice after this command to encrypt the file
(file with .cpt extention is encrypted)

// To decrypt the file

$ ccdecrypt <filename>

enter the decryption key (key used at the time of encryption)

// To open encrypted file 

$ ccat <filename>

enter the decryption key (key used at the time of encryption)

the screenshort are provided for proof 
